Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心理作用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我安份点\N马上就会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第141话 被释放的妖马炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才不是才吃过鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又没有吃到饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话\N就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着什么吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N我是没有带什么啦  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有饭吃了\N吃饭  吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  神官大人被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是指最近频传的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门杀害那些\N道行高深的神官和僧人这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道\N到底是什么人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一直发展到现在\N事情绝不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为这样\N被封印在神社里的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每到晚上就出来作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以村子才这么荒凉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有气味\N虽然只是杂碎妖怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我\N我一招就把他们通通解决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样的事情\N在这附近经常发生是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  到处都是这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛抢我的  还我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高僧和神官\N接二连三地遭到杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手好像是一个\N抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么听来\N那个女人想必是神乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个时候\N还以人类为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正如果这件事跟\N奈落那个家伙扯上关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不能袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在神乐在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个倒不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近最有名气的僧人\N或神官是哪一位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是问还在世的高僧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近还活着的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来最有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是万愿寺的神泉和尚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉和尚?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指那位神泉和尚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听过他的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N是一位很有名的僧人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说论起封印妖怪的功力\N无人能出其右啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连身为驱魔师的我也听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是非常有名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是封印了那个\N人称炼狱鬼的食人妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他骑的妖马“炎蹄”\N这个传说是最为有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您怎么了吗  神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…可能是我多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像感觉到炎蹄在嘶鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是封印在\N我们后山祠堂的妖马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄正如其名\N是一匹有着火焰马蹄的马妖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是传说中能够日行千里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚力非凡的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据传说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相隔百年前有一匹神马\N被卷入大火之中死去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的怨灵出现在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且随着火山爆发\N转生成为炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  都还不清楚咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过传说还不只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于炎蹄还有另外一个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑上炎蹄的话\N就能够取得天下?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么人传开的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这种说法广为流传
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然这种说法\N只不过是一种迷信罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为了炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类跟妖怪之间的争斗\N却没有停止过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了跟人类与妖怪\N无数次的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后生存下来的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄给予他骑上它的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得到了炎蹄的炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得气势逼人狂暴无比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为炼狱鬼的四处作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让村民们感到痛苦不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是拜托了神泉和尚\N为他们驱魔除妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我跟炼狱鬼的战斗\N持续了三天三夜的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了要封印炎蹄\N耗个三天三夜也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易\N打败了这两个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且分别封印在\N两个不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个祠堂也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说起来\N已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉和尚能够打败\N如此厉害妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一位非常了不起的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过既然是能够\N封印那种妖怪的和尚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐会盯上他\N也没什么好奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N既然如此我们快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间在这里磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爱使唤别人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么地方不对劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都没有感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座寺庙的附近\N有邪气正在逼近当中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快点去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟之前的那些家伙比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像稍微厉害了一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身吧  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为是的布下结界了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说杀害高僧的妖怪\N是个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们杀害了\N那些僧人跟神官的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这个婴儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个女人\N恐怕还要凶恶好几倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我窥视到\N此世与彼世的交界处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和尚  下一招你还避得开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这一招又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙蛇之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好地来窥视你的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成…功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…毕竟也老了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神泉师父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子…恐怕不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上有香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事的地点恐怕是寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神乐下的手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还留有那家伙的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下手的\N是一个抱着婴儿的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父很勇敢地\N跟那个妖怪战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜为了保护\N我们两个人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易\N把两个妖怪其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个婴儿成功地消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父的法力将他劈成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个婴儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落在白灵山之中\N再次诞生出来的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在白灵山魔塌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还特地带那个婴儿逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落来说\N他应该是相当重要的存在对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  总觉得没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最猛胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想带我去什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落派你来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成\N你是代替奈落来教训我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个由神乐来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正迟早有一天\N会变成这个样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窥视此世与彼世的交界处?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀了师父之前\N那个婴儿就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么窥视心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐和婴儿\N到处杀害神官和高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来觉得是为了\N把被封印住的妖怪们给解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来似乎没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此世与彼世的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是那个妖怪的封印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后山是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们师父\N好不容易用他的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印住的一匹\N叫做炎蹄的妖马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个叫炼狱鬼\N所骑的那匹妖马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  你们也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是犬夜叉  那匹妖马…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好跟它算个帐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这里来了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  既然如此我就用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那匹马冲来冲去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别管我\N一定要想办法阻止那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本就瞄不准
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点阻止\N那匹妖马的行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它停止移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候干嘛阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  大家快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它一定是想要去找\N被封印的主人炼狱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快点追吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下一半\N是要我怎么处理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点气息都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:19.77,ED,,0,0,0,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:35.82,ED,,0,0,0,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:41.89,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:45.42,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:51.62,ED,,0,0,0,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:24:01.89,ED,,0,0,0,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:09.84,ED,,0,0,0,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.94,ED,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:17.62,ED,,0,0,0,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:24.02,ED,,0,0,0,,So Come my way
